---
// Componente About
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background effects -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-secondary to-secondary/90"></div>
  
  <!-- Partículas decorativas -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10">
    <div class="hidden lg:block absolute top-20 right-20 w-20 h-20 rounded-full border border-primary/30 opacity-20 animate-rotate-slow"></div>
    <div class="hidden lg:block absolute bottom-40 left-20 w-32 h-32 rounded-full border border-blue-500/20 opacity-30 animate-rotate-slow" style="animation-direction: reverse; animation-duration: 25s;"></div>
    <div class="hidden lg:block absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/3 w-4 h-4 bg-primary/30 rounded-full opacity-70 animate-float"></div>
    <div class="hidden lg:block absolute top-1/3 left-1/4 w-3 h-3 bg-blue-500/30 rounded-full opacity-70 animate-float" style="animation-delay: 1.5s;"></div>
    <div class="hidden lg:block absolute bottom-1/3 right-1/4 w-5 h-5 bg-indigo-500/30 rounded-full opacity-70 animate-float" style="animation-delay: 2.5s;"></div>
    
    <!-- Patrón de puntos decorativo -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-pattern opacity-5"></div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Líneas decorativas -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-blue-500/20 to-transparent"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-indigo-500/20 to-transparent"></div>
  
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-fade-in-up">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
        <span class="badge-shine">Conóceme</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 relative">
        <span class="text-white">Sobre</span>
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-blue-700"> Mí</span>
        <div class="absolute -right-8 top-0 w-6 h-6 text-blue-500 animate-pulse-slow hidden md:block">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
      </h2>
      <div class="w-24 h-1.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 rounded-full mx-auto mb-8"></div>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Desarrollador FullStack con pasión por la innovación tecnológica y el crecimiento profesional.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="relative">
          <!-- Marco decorativo -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 border-2 border-blue-500/30 rounded-xl transform translate-x-4 translate-y-4 backdrop-blur-sm"></div>
          
          <!-- Elementos decorativos adicionales -->
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-8 h-8 border-t-2 border-l-2 border-blue-500/40"></div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-8 h-8 border-b-2 border-r-2 border-blue-500/40"></div>
          
          <!-- Card principal -->
          <div class="relative z-10 glass-card p-8 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/10 hover-lift hover:border-blue-500/30 group">
            <!-- Efecto de brillo en hover -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 rounded-xl"></div>
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                <div class="bg-blue-500/20 p-3 rounded-lg mr-4 group-hover:bg-blue-500/30 transition-all duration-300 relative overflow-hidden">
                  <!-- Efecto de brillo en el icono -->
                  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/10 to-transparent shimmer-effect opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100"></div>
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors duration-300">Perfil Profesional</h3>
              </div>
              
              <p class="text-gray-300 border-l-2 border-blue-500/20 pl-4 group-hover:border-blue-500/40 transition-colors duration-300">
                Soy un Desarrollador FullStack recién graduado de DAM (Desarrollo de Aplicaciones Multiplataforma) y técnico en SIR/SMX con 2.5 años de experiencia en Barcelona.
              </p>
              
              <p class="text-gray-300 border-l-2 border-blue-500/20 pl-4 group-hover:border-blue-500/40 transition-colors duration-300">
                Actualmente trabajo como <span class="text-blue-400 font-medium">Desarrollador FullStack</span> en AgriNews, donde me estoy formando en <span class="text-blue-400 font-medium">.NET, IA y backend</span>. Mi objetivo es seguir creciendo profesionalmente y aportar soluciones innovadoras.
              </p>
              
              <div class="pt-6">
                <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 flex items-center">
                  <div class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-400 to-blue-600 rounded-full mr-2"></div>
                  Habilidades personales
                </h4>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                  <div class="bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-500/10 rounded-lg p-3 hover:bg-blue-900/30 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-all flex items-center group/skill">
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" />
                      </svg>
                    </div>
                    <span class="group-hover/skill:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Trabajo en equipo</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-500/10 rounded-lg p-3 hover:bg-blue-900/30 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-all flex items-center group/skill">
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z" />
                      </svg>
                    </div>
                    <span class="group-hover/skill:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Comunicación</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-500/10 rounded-lg p-3 hover:bg-blue-900/30 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-all flex items-center group/skill">
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
                      </svg>
                    </div>
                    <span class="group-hover/skill:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Resolución de problemas</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-500/10 rounded-lg p-3 hover:bg-blue-900/30 hover:border-blue-500/30 transition-all flex items-center group/skill">
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15" />
                      </svg>
                    </div>
                    <span class="group-hover/skill:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Adaptabilidad</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay: 200ms;">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="glass-card p-6 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/10 hover-lift hover:border-blue-500/30 group hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-blue-500/10 transition-all duration-300">
            <!-- Efecto de brillo en hover -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 rounded-xl"></div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <div class="bg-blue-900/30 w-12 h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4 group-hover:bg-blue-900/50 transition-colors duration-300 relative overflow-hidden">
                <!-- Efecto de brillo en el icono -->
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/10 to-transparent shimmer-effect opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100"></div>
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h.01M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors duration-300">Experiencia laboral</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 border-l-2 border-blue-500/20 pl-4 group-hover:border-blue-500/40 transition-colors duration-300">
              2.5 años de experiencia como desarrollador y administrador de sistemas, trabajando en diversas empresas y proyectos con tecnologías modernas.
            </p>
            
            <!-- Badge decorativo -->
            <div class="mt-4 flex">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-blue-900/30 border border-blue-500/20 text-blue-300 flex items-center gap-1.5">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-400 animate-pulse"></span>
                2.5 años de experiencia
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="glass-card p-6 rounded-xl border border-indigo-500/10 hover-lift hover:border-indigo-500/30 group hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-indigo-500/10 transition-all duration-300">
            <!-- Efecto de brillo en hover -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 rounded-xl"></div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <div class="bg-indigo-900/30 w-12 h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4 group-hover:bg-indigo-900/50 transition-colors duration-300 relative overflow-hidden">
                <!-- Efecto de brillo en el icono -->
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/10 to-transparent shimmer-effect opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100"></div>
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-indigo-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5z" />
                  <path d="M12 14l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998a12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14z" />
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5zm0 0l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998a12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14zm-4 6v-7.5l4-2.222" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white group-hover:text-indigo-400 transition-colors duration-300">Formación académica</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 border-l-2 border-indigo-500/20 pl-4 group-hover:border-indigo-500/40 transition-colors duration-300">
              Graduado en Desarrollo de Aplicaciones Multiplataforma (DAM) y técnico en Sistemas y Redes, con formación continua en tecnologías emergentes.
            </p>
            
            <!-- Badge decorativo -->
            <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-indigo-900/30 border border-indigo-500/20 text-indigo-300">DAM</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-indigo-900/30 border border-indigo-500/20 text-indigo-300">SIR/SMX</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="glass-card p-6 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/10 hover-lift hover:border-purple-500/30 group hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-purple-500/10 transition-all duration-300">
            <!-- Efecto de brillo en hover -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 rounded-xl"></div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
              <div class="bg-purple-900/30 w-12 h-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-4 group-hover:bg-purple-900/50 transition-colors duration-300 relative overflow-hidden">
                <!-- Efecto de brillo en el icono -->
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/10 to-transparent shimmer-effect opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100"></div>
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-purple-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white group-hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors duration-300">Objetivos profesionales</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 border-l-2 border-purple-500/20 pl-4 group-hover:border-purple-500/40 transition-colors duration-300">
              Especializarme en desarrollo full stack con tecnologías modernas, profundizando en la integración de IA en aplicaciones web y contribuir a proyectos innovadores.
            </p>
            
            <!-- Badge decorativo -->
            <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-purple-900/30 border border-purple-500/20 text-purple-300 flex items-center gap-1.5">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-3 w-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
                </svg>
                Desarrollo Full Stack
              </span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs rounded-full bg-purple-900/30 border border-purple-500/20 text-purple-300 flex items-center gap-1.5">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-3 w-3" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
                </svg>
                IA
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 